      "en": "Volume 4 Annals 4: Emperor Shao",
      "raw": "卷四 本紀第四 少帝 Volume 4 Annals 4: Emperor Shao"
    },
    "sentenceCount": 149,
    "translatedCount": 0,
    "glossarySize": 33998,
    "scrapedAt": "2026-04-25T21:20:52.414Z",
